Remarks/Remarques: New curve #31.00 developed for 2023.  This curve shows a small change/refinement in the low to medium water section of curve.  This curve change was based on 4 open water measurements taken in 2023.
New curve #30.00 developed for 2020.  This curve shows a small change/refinement on low end from previous curve #29.00 due to 2020 measurements. Slight change occurred at GH 0.644 and below.
New curve #29.00 developed for 2019.  This curve shows a small change/refinement from previous curve #28.00 due to 2019 measurements. Slight change occurred at GH 0.784 and below.

New curve #28.00 developed for 2018.  This curve shows a small change/refinement from previous curve #27.00 due to 2018 measurements. Slight change occurred at medium stage and also an extension at both the high and low ends of curve to cover range for 2018.

Curve # 27 was developed starting high water event Oct 11 2016, where the MM taken in 2016 after this event plotted 11.5 % off rating, this result was confirmed with 2017 May MM at similar height. Thus refinement was need above 1.100 meters
